API is created which perform certain tasks :

   - Create a story
   - Fetch the story details
   - Fetch the story details with paragraphs and sentences


Tech stack and tools used :

    - Golang
    - PostgresQL
    - Pgadmin
    - Postman

Package  :

    - go get github.com/lib/pq

Databse :

    - User should have postgresql installed
    - User Should import the attached "sql" file before making requests


Postman Collection Link :

    - https://www.getpostman.com/collections/c7227ccbd406f0bd0172


How to run the server :

    - go run story.go    

